- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a machine learning model for relation learning. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with the integration of multi-modal signals in social network analysis. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques in social network analysis.
